      <h1>
        <span class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden"> Advent calendar 2024</span>

      </h1>
      
      

      <a href="/content/list-by-author/">
        </a>
    </div>
  </header>

  
  <div class="node__content">
    
            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item"><div class="view-header"><p>In this year's advent calendar we revisit some of our favourite episodes of our <em>Maths on the move</em> podcast! We're lucky to get to speak to lots of interesting mathematicians throughout the year, and our podcast captures many of those fascinating conversations, explores the maths people do, and why they love doing it.</p><p>Whether it's the wonders of AI, the uncertainty of chance, or the beauty of pure maths, we hope you enjoy this selection of <em>Maths on the move</em> episodes!</p></div></div>
      
  </div>
</article>

